    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:72ch;">PS-series errors are payroll-specific and usually involve the payroll service subscription, the tax-table download, or paycheck-processing validation. Often resolvable by verifying subscription status before assuming a deeper problem.</p>
